OL,3,CAbuse survivor: 'I'd wear t-shirt in
OL,4,Chope someone notices bruises'
OL,6,FA woman from who was abused by her
OL,7,Fpartner over several months has
OL,8,Fwelcomed the creation of a new scheme
OL,9,Fto help others spot the signs of
OL,10,Fdomestic violence.
OL,12,FDozens of businesses and their staff
OL,13,Fmembers are being trained to look for
OL,14,Fwarning signs.
OL,16,FRecalling her experience of an abusive
OL,17,Frelationship, Grace Shearer says she
OL,18,Ffelt trapped and that she could not
OL,19,Fask for help.
