OL,6,FShe has chosen to wave her right of
OL,7,Flifetime anonymity to speak out in the
OL,8,Fhope it helps others.
OL,10,FGrace explains: "I was pushed into a
OL,11,Fkitchen countertop and given quite a
OL,12,Flarge bruise.
OL,14,F"He would often pull the duvet cover
OL,15,Facross me which, on occasion, would
OL,16,Fgive me nasty friction burns on my
OL,17,Fneck.
OL,19,F"He'd often leave fingerprint bruise
OL,20,Fmarks on my arm.
