OL,3,CAbuse survivor: 'I'd wear t-shirt in
OL,4,Chope someone notices bruises'
OL,6,F"He'd push me, he'd pull me, he'd
OL,7,Foften pull me by my hair as well.
OL,9,F"If I had a bruise on my arm, I'd wear
OL,10,Fa t-shirt that I knew could ride up
OL,11,Fand had the possibility of showing a
OL,12,Fbruise, almost in the hope that if
OL,13,Fsomeone I knew had safeguarding
OL,14,Ftraining, they would notice it and do
OL,15,Fsomething."
OL,17,FIn May 2023, after months of abuse,
OL,18,Fthe neighbours heard Grace's screams
OL,19,Fand called the police.
