OL,6,FHer partner was subsequently convicted
OL,7,Fof offences amounting to domestic
OL,8,Fabuse at Guernsey's Royal Court.
OL,10,FGrace's hope is that by sharing her
OL,11,Fstory and through Safer Guernsey's new
OL,12,Fscheme, people can recognise the signs
OL,13,Fthat might signal someone is being
OL,14,Fabused.
OL,16,FThe charity will offer guidance and
OL,17,Fsupport to anyone who comes forward
OL,18,Ffor help.
