OL,6,FTraining officer Antonia Rainbow adds:
OL,7,F"We know that a lot of victims are
OL,8,Fisolated.
OL,10,F"Businesses and workplaces can be the
OL,11,Fonly people that actually interact
OL,12,Fwith someone in their daily lives,
OL,13,Foutside of their relationship.
OL,15,F"We're now targeting hairdressers,
OL,16,Fpeople who you actually spend some
OL,17,Ftime with, build a relationship with.
